      <title>标普称加州野火威胁全州房屋价值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/california-wildfires-threaten-home-values-across-state-s-p-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级表示，洛杉矶地区野火发生后，保险费上涨加剧了加州的负担能力危机，加州各地的房价可能面临下行压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/california-wildfires-threaten-home-values-across-state-s-p-says</guid>
